works.description: We have earlier seen customized Bugatti models in the form of Bugatti Veyron Pur Sung, that came with a 2 tone aluminum and carbon theme, and limited edition Pink Bugatti Veyron used by Japanese street wear Bathing Ape for its promotional activities. Now, the latest addition is the Bugatti Veyron Grand Sport with porcelain trimming on its body and even inside the cabin.
